1. Install Hadoop 2 (hadoop-2.5.0-cdh5.3.2)
2. download TFIDF.jar
3. Make Directory on HDFS
	hadoop fs -mkdir /user/hadoop/input
4. Use load_data.sh to put the dataset on HDFS folder created.
5. Run the TFIDF.jar
        hadoop jar /home/.../TFIDF.jar tfidf.TfidfAggregator /user/hadoop/input output

6. Read the output on HDFS
	
	


